-Hairstyle-for-Men.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prettydesigns.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2FShort-Korean-Hairstyle-for-Men.jpg&h=45108710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者咁，都幾似，我依家都係耷哂....但我前額頭髮呈大S曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://0.tqn.com/d/menshair/1/S/a/9/-/-/Drake-Bell.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F0.tqn.com%2Fd%2Fmenshair%2F1%2FS%2Fa%2F9%2F-%2F-%2FDrake-Bell.jpg&h=10c2bcf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想gel成點<br />\n我都唔太知邊D岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢隻幾靚，我都可以咁分界<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.readhouse.net/20161221/14822917646637125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.readhouse.net%2F20161221%2F14822917646637125.jpg&h=4156fad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hair-map.com/post/photo/normal/9898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hair-map.com%2Fpost%2Fphoto%2Fnormal%2F9898.jpg&h=1d515539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實我想聽下suggestions"},{"pid":"481044f285dcaf99dbb05e6eccde18e661297c57","tid":357643,"uid":129014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喂都要講下想gel咩頭</blockquote><br />\n同你咩髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原本應該係咁，但我唔高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.prettydesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Short-Korean-Hairstyle-for-Men.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prettydesigns.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2FShort-Korean-Hairstyle-for-Men.jpg&h=45108710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者咁，都幾似，我依家都係耷哂....但我前額頭髮呈大S曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://0.tqn.com/d/menshair/1/S/a/9/-/-/Drake-Bel